OL,8,     Fscooters.
OL,9,G0800 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,10,     FWe meet sunchaser John Hamill, who
OL,11,     Fruns the longest established
OL,12,     FBritish fish and chip shop on the
OL,13,     FCosta Del Sol six days a week. And
OL,14,     Fon the seventh he sells
OL,15,     Fbric-a-brac.
OL,16,G0900 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,17,     FWe meet couple Deb and Dave who
OL,18,     Ftraded in the delights of Essex
OL,19,     Ffor a home in a beautiful 'pueblo
OL,20,     Fblanco' or traditional white
OL,21,     Fvillage on a mountain overlooking
OL,22,     Fthe Mediterranean.
