OL,5,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,6,     FThe staff and patients of
OL,7,     FBarnsley's A&E department are put
OL,8,     Funder the microscope. A man is
OL,9,     Ftreated after being involved in a
OL,10,     Fserious motorbike accident.
OL,11,G2100 999: Killer On The Line
OL,12,     FDominic Isom's 999 call reporting
OL,13,     Fhis fiancee Samantha Henderson
OL,14,     Fmissing sparks a manhunt in
OL,15,     FDorset. As her family supported
OL,16,     Fhim, Isom soon became the focus of
OL,17,     Fa murder investigation.
