OL,5,G2200 999: Critical Condition
OL,6,     FOn the front line at Birmingham's
OL,7,     FQueen Elizabeth Hospital. A man
OL,8,     Ffalls from scaffold, impaling
OL,9,     Fhimself on a flagpole, and a
OL,10,     F73-year-old faces life-changing
OL,11,     Finjuries.
OL,12,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,13,     FDr Natalia Spierings helps Justin
OL,14,     Fwho has a genetic condition which
OL,15,     Fmeans his skin is covered in lumps
OL,16,     Fmade up of nerves. Dr Dev Shah is
OL,17,     Fasked to remove a cyst named
OL,18,     FEgbert.
