OL,6,     FConor Woodman is in Bangkok,
OL,7,     FThailand, one of the hottest
OL,8,     Fcities on earth.15 years since his
OL,9,     Flast visit, it's time to see if
OL,10,     Fthe gem scam he first encountered
OL,11,     Fthere is still being run.
